    skos:altLabel "hazard prediction"@en ;
    skos:definition "Hazard forecasts provide information on the physical event characteristics, such as the location, timing, and magnitude of a potentially damaging event (Merz et al., 2020 in Gill et al., 2022)."@en ;
    skos:inScheme <http://connectivity-hub.com/terms/> ;
